(Or the Railway production URL when deployed)

## File Descriptions

### Backend Files

**server.js** - Main Express server file
- Sets up middleware (CORS, body parser)
- Defines health check endpoint
- Defines /api/generate-test-cases endpoint
- Error handling and 404 routes

**claudeService.js** - Claude AI integration
- Calls Anthropic API to generate test cases
- Handles response formatting
- Returns structured test case objects

**testcaseroutes.js** - Test case routes (if used)
- API route definitions
- Request validation

### Frontend Files

**App.jsx** - Main React component
- Form for URL and test type input
- Handles API calls to backend
- Displays test cases in table format
- CSV and JSON download functionality

**App.css** - Styling for the application
- Beautiful gradient background
- Responsive form layout
- Table styling
- Download button styling

**main.jsx** - React entry point
- Mounts App component to DOM

**tailwind.config.js** - Tailwind CSS configuration
- Custom theme colors
- Responsive breakpoints

## Troubleshooting

### "Cannot find module 'claudeService'"
**Solution:** Make sure `backend/src/services/claudeService.js` exists

### "CORS error - Response to preflight request"
**Solution:** Check CORS_ORIGIN environment variable matches your frontend URL

### "Port 5000 already in use"
**Solution:** Change PORT in .env or kill the process using port 5000

### "Network Error in frontend"
**Solution:** Make sure backend is running and API URL is correct in App.jsx

### "API key not recognized"
**Solution:** Verify your CLAUDE_API_KEY is valid from https://console.anthropic.com/

